    {
      "id": 1,
      "slug": "welcome-intro-learning-objectives",
      "title": "歡迎、介紹和學習目標",
      "description_html": "",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "type": "image",
          "variant": "full",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "LIGHT",
            "card_mode": "WHITE",
            "image_opacity": 0.5,
            "image_opacity_color": "#000000",
            "zoom_on_click": false,
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 0,
            "padding_bottom": 0,
            "custom_padding_top": 0,
            "custom_padding_bottom": 0,
            "entrance_animation": true
          },
          "image_role": "decorative",
          "media": {
            "path": "resources/images/intro-1.png",
            "alt": "Intro_1.png",
            "source_asset": "Intro_1.png",
            "mime_type": "image/png",
            "bytes": 93469,
            "dimensions": {
              "originalWidth": 1680,
              "originalHeight": 222
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "type": "text",
          "variant": "subheading",
          "style": {
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "heading_html": "<p>在本模塊結束時，您將能夠：</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "list",
          "variant": "bulleted",
          "style": {
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "list_style": "bulleted",
          "items_html": [
            "<p>解釋向 ORW 的過渡及其對 AI 效率和可擴展性的影響。 &nbsp;</p>",
            "<p>確定ORW結構、有效負載選項、兼容性和可持續性特徵。 &nbsp;</p>",
            "<p>定義電源完整性、100A 排序和高功率機架共享基線。</p>"
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "type": "divider",
          "variant": "divider",
          "style": {
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "type": "text",
          "variant": "paragraph",
          "style": {
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "body_html": "<p>隨著人工智能需求的加速，標準的600毫米機架造成了嚴重的<strong>物理瓶頸</strong>。本模塊探討 OCP 社區 &nbsp; 如何響應 1200 毫米 ORW 框架。</p><p>您將瞭解該標準如何發展，通過更智能的電力傳輸、穩健的結構設計和可擴展的基礎設施來滿足下一代要求。</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 6,
          "type": "image",
          "variant": "hero",
          "style": {
            "image_size": "large",
            "image_opacity": 0.5,
            "image_opacity_color": "#000000",
            "zoom_on_click": true,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "image_role": "content",
          "media": {
            "path": "resources/images/x-8dc63f.jpg",
            "alt": "標準機架與 Open Rack Wide 的寬度比較",
            "source_asset": "X-#8DC63F.jpg",
            "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
            "bytes": 115597,
            "dimensions": {
              "originalWidth": 1343,
              "originalHeight": 1080
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": 7,
          "type": "quote",
          "variant": "d",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "LIGHT",
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "quote_html": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 2.1rem\"><em>特別感謝 AMD 的 PMTS 系統架構師 Eduardo Estrada 提供的技術指導和意見，這對本課程的開發起到了重要作用。</em></span></p>",
