          "body_html": "<p>向高密度 AI 機架供電需要強大的電氣連接。 ORW 框架使用標準化接口來安裝 48V 母線，確保與高功率機架共享基線的無縫互操作性。</p><p>單擊每個選項卡瞭解更多信息。</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "accordion",
          "variant": "accordion",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1e1e1e",
            "zoom_on_click": false,
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "title": "標準化母線安裝",
              "description_html": "<p>用於母線安裝的框架接口與 ORV3 HPR 母線接口相同。</p>",
              "media": {
                "path": "resources/images/untitled-design-49.jpg",
                "alt": "Untitled design (49).png",
                "source_asset": "Untitled design (49).jpg",
                "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
                "bytes": 100049,
                "dimensions": {
                  "width": 1680,
                  "height": 944,
                  "originalWidth": 1680,
                  "originalHeight": 1680
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "100A 連續電源路徑",
              "description_html": "<p>IT Gear 輸入連接器具有主電源路徑和電源返回路徑，其額定連續電流至少為 100A。</p>",
              "media": {
                "path": "resources/images/untitled-design-50.jpg",
                "alt": "Untitled design (50).png",
                "source_asset": "Untitled design (50).jpg",
                "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
                "bytes": 38421,
                "dimensions": {
                  "originalWidth": 1680,
                  "originalHeight": 1680
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "電源排序和傳感",
              "description_html": "<p>新連接器要求 IT 設備設計使用電源檢測線來控制電源輸入電路的開和關行為，防止危險的電弧事件。</p>",
              "media": {
                "path": "resources/images/it-gear-input-connector.png",
                "alt": "IT Gear Input Connector.png",
                "source_asset": "IT Gear Input Connector.png",
                "mime_type": "image/png",
                "bytes": 33471,
                "dimensions": {
                  "originalWidth": 541,
                  "originalHeight": 512
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "差分電壓檢測",
              "description_html": "<p>這個可選但強烈推薦的功能允許設施監控輸入電源電纜組件的電壓降，從而增強熱事件緩解。</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
