            "entrance_animation": true
          },
          "image_role": "decorative",
          "media": {
            "path": "resources/images/black-banner-intro-1.png",
            "alt": "Black banner - intro.png",
            "source_asset": "Black banner - intro-1.png",
            "mime_type": "image/png",
            "bytes": 12283,
            "dimensions": {
              "originalWidth": 1680,
              "originalHeight": 295
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "knowledge_check",
          "variant": "multiple_choice",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1e1e1e",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "question_type": "multiple_choice",
          "question_html": "<p>為什麼 ORW 基本規格從機架設計中消除了標準滾動腳輪？</p>",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text_html": "<p>為更大的液體冷卻歧管騰出空間。</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>直接在結構平臺上安全支撐高達 3,500 公斤的重量。</p>",
              "correct": true
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>確保與較舊的 19 英寸 IT 設備兼容。</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>降低底座的整體製造成本。</p>",
              "correct": false
            }
          ],
          "feedback_correct_html": "<p>正確！由於滿載的 ORW 機架重達 3,500 公斤，因此標準腳輪不再是安全的選擇。機架直接位於結構平臺上，以實現最大穩定性。</p>",
          "feedback_incorrect_html": "<p>標準腳輪會在 3,500 公斤的人工智能集群的巨大重量下彎曲。 ORW 框架設計為直接位於結構平臺上。</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "type": "knowledge_check",
          "variant": "multiple_choice",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1e1e1e",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "question_type": "multiple_choice",
          "question_html": "<p>對還是錯？ Open Rack Wide 框架僅支持 OpenU 垂直間距。</p>",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text_html": "<p>真</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>假</p>",
              "correct": true
            }
          ],
          "feedback_correct_html": "<p>正確！ ORW 框架支持 OU 和 RU 垂直間距。它包括用於支撐支架的特定切口，以允許混合各種類型的 IT 設備。</p>",
          "feedback_incorrect_html": "<p>不正確。基本規範要求 ORW 框架必須通過不同的支架支持 OU 和 RU 垂直間距。</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "type": "knowledge_check",
          "variant": "multiple_choice",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1e1e1e",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "question_type": "multiple_choice",
          "question_html": "<p>Open Rack V3 IT 設備輸入連接器上的主電源和返回路徑的最小連續額定電流是多少？</p>",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text_html": "<p>200A連續</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>150A連續</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>100A連續</p>",
              "correct": true
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>50A連續</p>",
              "correct": false
            }
          ],
          "feedback_correct_html": "<p>正確！輸入連接器上的電源路徑和電源返回路徑的額定連續電流必須至少為 100A。</p>",
          "feedback_incorrect_html": "<p>不正確。輸入連接器要求主電源和電源返回路徑的最小額定值為 100A 連續電流。</p>"
        },
        {
